terministic path per artifact or decision. Leave clear evidence of actions taken, files or issues touched, remaining blockers, and verification performed. If writing a report, write the latest PM report to docs/team/outputs/pm.md. Do not run another Handrail team role, manually launch another role, call app-server thread creation, edit automation records, or edit automation database rows as a handoff mechanism. Then stop.","rollout_path":"/Users/velocityworks/.codex/sessions/2026/05/01/rollout-2026-05-01T18-29-13-019de5a9-0921-7122-b975-67bd5d0a451b.jsonl","created_at":"2026-05-01 22:29:13","updated_at":"2026-05-01 22:54:22"},
